Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates who are after the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...head for the New World, the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,However, no one has ever fully explored it except for Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined many pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They landed on Punk Hazard;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,an island with two parts, one burning, the other frozen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and learned about the ruler of the island - Caesar Clown's motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All while trying to escape Shinokuni,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,they are heading to R Building with the children that they rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, a climactic battle rages on-- between Luffy and Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:49.25,"Sign",,0,0,0,,LAND OF DEATH
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my scientific power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...the type of person that Luffy hates the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy won't forgive Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't ever wanna see your face again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...Grizzly Magnum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can work under me if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:04.90,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Raid! An Assassin from Dressrosa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:53.04,"Sign",,0,0,0,,VARIOUS PLACES IN THE NEW WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what they call a "public experiment"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He kicked Caesar's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama should know about this-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Joker is going to take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let "Jack" know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?! It's not gonna be pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they formed an alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the world know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not just a problem in the underground anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out! This place is gonna collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:34.04,"Sign",,0,0,0,,B BUILDING 2ND FLOOR
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Hurry up! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocha! You can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocha! You're gonna be alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Show some medical team guts, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chopper-yan! Are you sure this is the right way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:07:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta join the rest of our crew as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going straight and go down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the fastest way to R Building!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:14.12,"Sign",,0,0,0,,R BUILDING 2ND FLOOR - THE SECRET ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:13.03,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna shut the door to R building
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.12,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,before the gas flows in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Alright, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, you're almost there! Keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami, you're almost at R Building!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are just a bunch of guinea pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would care if hundreds of you die or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the dregs of society!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the Master was such an awful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who should we trust from now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This room is not gonna last very long, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I found the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more to go, Mocha! Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Brook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is serious! Kin'emon-san got...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon-san got harmed by the gas and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...died!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Brook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,While we were helping the children in the examination room evacuate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and looking for Kin'emon-san's son, we met a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:09:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Momonosuke turned to a small dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh! I shouldn't tell anybody but it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Corpse-dono! Maybe, the dragon I sliced up earlier was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done a terrible thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon-san, you can't go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That area is filled up with the gas by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The deadly gas is right in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My spirit will carry me through anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's fire or gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's impossible! Kin'emon-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And he ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! Don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go down the stairs right there and get into R Building!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The gas is really closing in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost at R Building! You can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there! Keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:26.71,"Sign",,0,0,0,,R BUILDING 1ST FLOOR
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! You're here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Brownbeard-cchi's on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean, he's not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The children!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Momo? I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends are on their way to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They always keep their word!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:11:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Get to where Nami-san and the others are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,--This way! --Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see R Building!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper and the others are not there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He was giving the girl first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can he make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys okay?! Good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoker-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.79,"Sign",,0,0,0,,THE PATH BETWEEN BUILDING R AND D
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we really need this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the truck that they use to transport containers of SAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna let everybody ride it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This laboratory will collapse soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to escape as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hatter! {Straw Hat-ya}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tra-guy! Smokey! I didn't expect you to come from that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Smo-yan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's Smo-yan! --Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Smo-yan! I'm so glad! We have so much to report!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop screaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where did Caesar go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I kicked his ass and he got blown away along with the door that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How far did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You... Our plan was to kidnap him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't even wanna catch that bastard anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the plan if you like it or not! What are you gonna do if he runs away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about that jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can just change a plan as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have trusted you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats have foiled the plans
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of Master Caesar Clown, scientist and ruler of Punk Hazard Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,However, A Building has filled up with Shinokuni, the deadly gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, B Building is almost filled as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, Caesar's laboratory has started collapsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Brook! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The only exit to escape from the laboratory as well
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,as the island is the "R-66" door in R Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Brownbeard-cchi, for a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper will take care of you soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think they are alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they will get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:15:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, before the showdown between Luffy and Caesar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In the sky near Punk Hazard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:15.53,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,The end of this mission is the end of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:18.84,"Sign",,0,0,0,,DON QUIXOTE PIRATES - A SERVANT / AN ASSASSIN BABY 5
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:18.84,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,I'll finish him off when I get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Joker! What an asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed my sweet fiancé by destroying the whole town!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the eighth time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed eight men that I loved and made a commitment to,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroyed eight towns!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he want to screw up my happiness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:44.03,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Because the Young Master loves you-dasuyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:51.63,"Sign",,0,0,0,,DON QUIXOTE PIRATES - A COMBATANT BUFFALO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:47.20,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,He loves you like his own sister
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:49.71,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,so he doesn't begrudge destroying a town
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:51.63,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,or two-dasuyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to learn to say "No"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:16:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What was wrong with him?! He needed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell in love with you at first sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ten days later, he became the eighth victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't have loved me in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When someone asks you something, you can't say "No."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird to subscribe to 50 different newspapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You lend others too much money!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You are forced to buy so much stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How much debt do you have now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business! About 98 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! Can I borrow 2 million berries?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:16:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... When do you need it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When I go back, I wanna hit a casino!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then, I'll get it ready for you as soon as we complete our mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry out this mission because he asked me but I'll kill Joker at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Punk Hazard-dasuyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The island is covered in Caesar's gas and I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it go away if I fire this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you hop off and wait for me, Baby 5?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold! My typhoon-like power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Gust - Matasaburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's wait there until Caesar, Monet, and Vergo come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna get back quick to play roulette at a casino-dasuyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The tanker exploded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Something hit it-dasuyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a human! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Caesar Clown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:04.09,"Sign",,0,0,0,,DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:05.07,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:06.96,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Ring, ring... Clank!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Joker! This is Buffalo from Punk Hazard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Joker! We just arrived at Punk Hazard-dasuyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what's going on but we just saw Master Caesar...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...getting blown out of the building, injured-dasuyan!--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Recover Caesar immediately and come back to Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! We'll recover Caesar-dasuyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Monet and Vergo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a reason. Let's do as he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, squirts! Luck is on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I have Caesar in my custody, he can create SAD for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you all! We got to go! Get on the truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened to him-dasuyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Do you see someone on the deck of the tanker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think no one could survive that gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A robot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that strange bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.59,0:23:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In Building R, which is on the verge of collapse...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...Luffy waits intently for his crewmates to wrap things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,with the help of some powerful Devil Fruit powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.93,0:23:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...Baby 5 and Buffalo attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.03,0:23:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,General Franky alone confronts them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Running Wild! Invincible General Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
